1
00:00:07,416 --> 00:00:13,129
You can see guru according to
the inner awakenment of the disciple.

2
00:00:13,129 --> 00:00:16,109
[The Guru is Not a Picture]

3
00:00:16,109 --> 00:00:19,043
The guru is not a picture.

4
00:00:19,043 --> 00:00:21,052
And Guru Mahārāj makes the the obvious point,

5
00:00:21,052 --> 00:00:23,285
he said, “What if you have pictures of the guru

6
00:00:23,285 --> 00:00:28,889
from when he was twenty, twenty-five,
thirty, thirty-five, forty, etc.,

7
00:00:29,230 --> 00:00:33,021
and the form is changing dramatically,

8
00:00:33,021 --> 00:00:35,115
then which one?”

9
00:00:35,115 --> 00:00:37,138
What is Guru?

10
00:00:37,138 --> 00:00:43,137
Is Guru that form you saw at twenty,
twenty-five, fifty …?

11
00:00:43,137 --> 00:00:47,005
As we saw, the picture of
Bhakti Vinod Ṭhākur with the big beard.

12
00:00:47,036 --> 00:00:49,634
And Gurudev once said,
on his veranda in Kolkata,

13
00:00:49,634 --> 00:00:53,829
he said, “And to think, he’s a
thirteen-year-old girl in the spiritual world”,

14
00:00:54,028 --> 00:00:57,908
but he’s sitting there with the beard.

15
00:00:57,908 --> 00:00:59,567
So he’s talking about his svarūp,

16
00:00:59,567 --> 00:01:02,207
and his highest expression
in the spiritual domain.

17
00:01:02,207 --> 00:01:05,886
So it’s according to the inner
awakenment of the disciple

18
00:01:05,886 --> 00:01:10,012
that they have some depth of seeing guru.

